rows.label: tev058001_SEL1031
rows.name: Ask Mumun about the indigens in Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0011
rows.name:
Mumun hear that Prone are weak against beam
weapons.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0012
rows.name:
Mumun not really know how to use those,
but maybe friend can handle them?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0013
rows.name:
If so, go out and lay hurt on every Prone that comes
sniffing around door of friend.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0014
rows.name:
Friend needs to show zero-tolerance policy to bullies
who rough up poor innocent Nopon![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0018
rows.name: Mgaaah! Mumun gave in! Mumun gave in![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0019
rows.name:
Business take backbone. Mujiji practically beat this
mantra into poor Mumun. But when Mumun came
face-to-face with muscleheads... Meeeeeeeh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0020
rows.name:
Next time, Mumun going to swap in some kind of
lookalike fruit and deliver that instead.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0021
rows.name:
Prone too stupid to read label on box anyway!
Meh heh heh heh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0023
rows.name:
Sphinx underneath Victory Rock is like king of all
dangerous creatures in area.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0024
rows.name:
Even toughest monster makes sure to kowtow when
tiptoeing past king![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0025
rows.name:
Dorian Caravan always go through lots of trouble to
avoid royal turf of king.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0026
rows.name:
So if friend can make problem go away,
Mumun would be VERY grateful.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_SEL2011
rows.name: Ask Mumun for information about enemies in Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Mumun about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0022
rows.name:
For while there, Mumun thought Prone were going to
take over Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0027
rows.name:
Good thing tough friends were around to be Nopon
bodyguards![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0028
rows.name:
Mumun hear that Prone are weak against beam
weapons.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0034
rows.name:
Does Earth friend have one? If so, go out there and
blast Prone bullies to bits! Ker-pow![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0029
rows.name:
Friends SURVIVED?! Mumun starting to wonder if
Ganglion pursuers ripped poor friends to shreds.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0030
rows.name:
Mumun have many close calls as well.
Almost got eaten 382 times before making it home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0031
rows.name:
Out of those, Mumun end up in mouth 74 times and
stomach 16 times. Smell was really, really horrible.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0032
rows.name:
Meh! Eureka! Mumun need to find way to smell bad!
Then no one try to eat Mumun![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058001_MSG0033
rows.name:
Genius Mumun just strike on major business
opportunity...[ST:wait ]
